  <Subject Subject_ID="300264628">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300162797</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>grinding and milling machinery [300162797], grinding and milling equipment [300024716], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to machines or mechanical apparatus, either simple or complex, for grinding or reducing a solid substance to a powder or pulp, such as corn or spice. To refer to the combined building and the milling machinery housed within it, use "mills (buildings)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar eenvoudige of complexe machines of mechanische apparaten die worden gebruikt om vaste stoffen, zoals graan of kruiden, te verpulveren of tot poeder of pulp te vermalen. Gebruik 'molens (gebouwen)' om te verwijzen naar de combinatie van een gebouw en de daarin ondergebrachte maalinrichting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bezeichnet eine Maschine oder einen mechanischen Apparat, einfach oder komplex, zum Mahlen oder Zerkleinern einer festen Substanz zu Pulver oder Brei, beispielsweise Korn oder Gewürze. Für die Kombination von Gebäude und installierter Mühlentechnik ist "Mühle (Bauwerk)" zu verwenden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
